message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with sound and audio processing. cs.CV is also likely as it deals with image and video analysis, which could be used in conjunction with sound analysis for drone detection. cs.CR is another possibility as it deals with security and privacy, which is the motivation for detecting drones used for malicious purposes. cs.AI and cs.LG are less likely but still possible as they deal with machine learning and deep neural networks, which are the methods used in this paper.
